entries.journal_entry_description: A collector in the cantina needs trophies for his collection. Head up to the Atrium and start hunting!
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Wyle Artis needs you to go hunting in the Atrium. Take the Elevator to the upper level.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Atrium
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Wyle told you that he needs feathers from the Flits in the Atrium. Collect 4 Pristine Feathers.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Wyle Artis Needs Feathers from the Atrium
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Wyle Artis also needs lizard teeth for a necklace. Collect 7 usable teeth for him from the Scyks in the Atrium.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Wyle Artis Needs Lizard Teeth from the Atrium
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Now that you have the feathers and teeth for Wyle, use the elevator and return to the main level.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go back to the Main Level
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return to Wyle Artis in the cantina for your fee.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Return to Wyle Artis in the Cantina
